## Third-party model licenses

This repository contains Colab notebooks that download and use third-party
models. The MIT license above applies only to the notebook code itself;
model weights, datasets, and other artifacts are governed by their own
licenses. See each notebook's README section and the model's Hugging Face
page for commercial-use terms:

| Notebook | Model | License |
|----------|-------|---------|
| Pixal3D | [TencentARC/Pixal3D](https://github.com/TencentARC/Pixal3D) | MIT |
| Qwen3-TTS | [Qwen/Qwen3-TTS-12Hz](https://huggingface.co/Qwen) | Apache 2.0 |
| Higgs-Audio | [multimodalart/higgs-audio-v3](https://huggingface.co/multimodalart) | Research / Non-Commercial |
| MisoTTS | [MisoLabs/MisoTTS](https://huggingface.co/MisoLabs/MisoTTS) | Other (see model card) |
| Supertonic-3 | [Supertone/supertonic-3](https://huggingface.co/Supertone) | MIT code, OpenRAIL-M model |
| Dia | [nari-labs/dia](https://huggingface.co/nari-labs) | Apache 2.0 |
| IndicF5 | [ai4bharat/IndicF5](https://huggingface.co/ai4bharat) | MIT (gated) |
| MOSS-TTS | [OpenMOSS-Team/MOSS-TTS-v1.5](https://huggingface.co/OpenMOSS-Team) | Apache 2.0 |
| dots.tts-soar | [rednote-hilab/dots.tts-soar](https://huggingface.co/rednote-hilab) | Apache 2.0 |
| Fish S2 Pro | [fishaudio/s2-pro](https://huggingface.co/fishaudio) | Fish Audio Research (non-commercial) |

Reference voice clips in `TTS_Voice_Library.ipynb` are public-domain or
permissively licensed (CC-BY, CC-BY-4.0, MIT, Unlicense). See the per-clip
metadata in the notebook for source attribution.
